snippet.title: Poochy & Yoshi’s Woolly World – On your mark… Get set…
snippet.description:
It’s a race to the finish for Yarn Yoshi and friends. Are you cheering for the underdog? Discover a wild and woolly world in Poochy & Yoshi’s Woolly World, releasing Feb. 3rd on Nintendo 3DS or try the eShop demo available at http://yoshiswoollyworld.nintendo.com/3ds/#/home/.

#PoochyAndYoshi #WoollyWorld

You can get Poochy & Yoshi's Woolly World here: https://goo.gl/54VUvU
